high_descs: Walk towards the fridge and then right towards the stove.
Pick up the left metal pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Place the pan on the top shelf inside the fridge, let it cool, and take the pan back out.
Turn right and walk towards the stove.
Place the pan back to the original spot.
anns.task_desc: Cool down a pan from the stove.

high_descs: Go straight to the fridge, the go right to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left on the stove.
Turn around and bring the pan to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Take the pan, turn right and bring it to the stove.
Put the pan back on the stove in the same spot.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.

high_descs: Walk forward to the refrigerator and then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the front, left burner.
Turn to the left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, place the pan inside, close the door, reopen the door, remove the pan, and close the door.
Turn around to the right and walk back to the stove.
Place the pan back on the front, left burner.
anns.task_desc: Replacing a cooled pan on a burner.
